  "title": "It's Just You and Me",
  "description": "Living in a dynamic and unpredictable world, we are all on a journey of continual reinvention. Sometimes change is welcomed and at other times, it is forced upon us by circumstance. What elements of ourselves do we choose to keep and which parts do we let go of? This contemporary dance show honours the many versions self.",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Stephanie Lilley<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Stephanie Lilley<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Sarah Adam, June Chen, Hannah Chyz, Ruby Chyz, Em Erickson, Allison San Martin Fini, Hannah Ilkiw, Stephanie Lilley, Rebecca McLeod, April Seburn, Jason Romero, Kelsey Wright<br/>",
  "website": "",
  "plain_language": "This contemporary dance show looks at how people change throughout their lives. It celebrates the different versions of people.",
